Instructions for Builing and Burning a Cobalt ROM:
--------------------------------------------------

To build the Cobalt x86 ROM, follow these steps:

1) in this cobalt-rom dir, symlink 'linux' to a rom-ready linux source tree
1) type 'make'
2) Watch the build process
3) Your ROM images are in the files cobalt*.rom

To clean up, type 'make clean'
To clean everything up, including the kernel symlink, type 'make distclean'
To clean the kernel, type 'make kclean'


